</ol>

<p>Pictured left: Heavy Duty Black Clothes Rails Garment Home Shop Storage Display, Complete Retail Source £22 ;  Right: Single Garment Rack, Onbuy, £169.43</p>

<p> 6. Right is more expensive </p>

<p>Pictured left: Nautical Wooden Ladder Shelves White from Dunelm, £45. Pictured right: Despagne Ladder Bookcase by August Grove, £946.49</p>

